
Metro Home Menu
---------------

An alternative home screen implementation based on the work by Sabish:



[http://forum.xbmc.org/showthread.php?tid=132897&pid=1351472#pid1351472](http://forum.xbmc.org/showthread.php?tid=132897&pid=1351472#pid1351472)



Enable this menu by selecting **"Enable horizontal Home Menu"** in the skin options. Don't forget to enable widgets!





